{"tid":760832,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇辦法可以令樓下班耆英唔好咁自私","createTime":"2018-07-30T01:43:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-30T03:08:06.000Z","uid":100417,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4998f44c784763af36b801090953bcb6dddd99e3","tid":760832,"uid":100417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T01:43:53.000Z","msg":"我屋企附近行大慨十分鐘會有三個羽毛球場，<br />\n都算係有蓋既好曬或者落雨都仲可以打到波，<br />\n屋企兩老因為平時返工小做運動又想健康啲，<br />\n呢排就開始落街去打下羽毛球，<br />\n但去左幾次就發現三個場基本上日日都比班耆英霸住哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢地每日5-6個人每日5點幾開始霸 到熄燈先走！ <br />\n佢地兩個人用哂成個場 有時企係到吹水又唔用 <br />\n叫佢借半邊玩下又步步相逼 係咁打埋你到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我都有諗過去體育館租場 兩老又話涼住冷氣打好似冇咁有效 想流多啲汗 所以都唔知點 <br />\n佢地有時霸兩個場 有時又霸哂三個場 <br />\n咁其他人基本上係唔洗用 放工返去都成7點啦<br />\n只係一齊放假可以陪兩老晏就打下波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0bc831c9395216df7dc05f22c11be9061a02ea7","tid":760832,"uid":34511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T01:50:09.000Z","msg":"帶班frd子去兇兩句都走啦"},{"pid":"9cbeb18799624caa0fc9584f0770bf01b4bcd0ae","tid":760832,"uid":78349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T01:51:06.000Z","msg":"住私樓叫管理員做野<br />\n住公屋就⋯⋯"},{"pid":"6aaccaa51443eed5aff57dda77923ca3fd213b5f","tid":760832,"uid":54481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T02:00:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://therightnewsnetwork.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/maxresdefault-1-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftherightnewsnetwork.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F03%2Fmaxresdefault-1-1.jpg&h=6730cd58&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"04bbaf341780ad34f89b6a24adb41466f2fbb5cc","tid":760832,"uid":54481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6aaccaa51443eed5aff57dda77